        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张天龙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂声黑贼哪里行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马前来的丑鬼，通名受死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么？他妈的。卫爷。你叫什样东西？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要问俺，俺乃人才驸马张天龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卫小申",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这个贼王八日的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你大不过我拳头，高不过我的膝盖，待你驸马擒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张天龙杀，张天龙下，卫小申追下。张天龙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这厮倒也厉害，用招魂旗擒他便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卫小申上，杀。张天龙用大手抓卫小申，卫小申下，狗形上，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你哪里走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓，跑了跑了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张天龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑蛋慢走，你驸马爷来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张天龙追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
