    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "杨仙童",
        "玉宝公主"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四手下引杨仙童同上，四女兵、玉宝公主同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两家交战同勒马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阵前来了一小娃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好似天宫小哪叱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看他不是凡人样"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站立阵前用目观，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那旁来了一婵娟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "聘婷容貌似天仙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨仙童、玉宝公主同杀，同下。四女兵、四手下同对把子，同下。杨仙童、玉宝公主同上，同杀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用动手咧。你叫什么名字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少爷杨仙童。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我杀来杀去，弄个稀烂，为的是什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺要你的命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我和你有冤？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无冤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有仇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既无冤仇，为什么要我的命呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺要扫尽番奴，保俺元帅回朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要保你家元帅回朝，我与你商量商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "商量什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我暂且收兵，咱们俩留个交情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们南朝人不懂交情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。南朝人连交情都不懂得，怎么好呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，附耳过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（玉宝公主附耳。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。我下山时节，师父言道：有花就采。莫非就此成功？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，你的帐房在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你瞧那黄罗帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我们驸马的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可是那张天龙？待我去毁了他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你毁不成他，再叫他干了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你瞧那红罗帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又是哪个的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我姐姐的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你姐姐比你长的怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个色鬼。你瞧那素罗帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巧了，素罗帐对我出家的劲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在素罗帐等你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "等我作什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与你开荤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今晚必来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来者君子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不来呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "玉宝公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玉堂春的儿子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨仙童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
